Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.50,0:01:23.34,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)\t(1300,2300,\3c&HAA813F&)}真真假假分辨不清
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.70,0:01:28.88,OPCN3,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}想要时刻在你身边　时刻守护着你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:33.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}除此之外别无他求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.88,0:01:34.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Catch you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.70,0:01:39.68,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}如果说　这都是你的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:40.16,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}Trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:44.72,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}若你想欺骗整个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.82,0:01:45.64,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}ooh baby
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.76,0:01:49.34,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}那我也甘愿背叛一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.50,0:02:00.52,OPCN3,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}我和你　在一起的时光虽不是永恒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:06.82,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}即使有一天我消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.00,0:02:11.62,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)\3c&H7FCC6D&\t(3100,4100,\3c&HAD3A7F&}在你的记忆中　我也从未褪色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.64,0:02:22.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}如果说　我如今感受到的幸福仅仅是幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:28.78,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}那么真正的爱又会在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.38,0:02:35.58,OPCN2,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,300)}我的心意　确确实实　传递给了你
